Fix the "Turn On" notification permission error and ensure "Reset All Data" clears the "Perfect Day" count.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The "Reset All Data" function will now clear **ALL** local storage for the app, including themes and other settings, to ensure a true clean slate.

